description:
The Word Sane is intended to link our awareness of the divine, when we are healthy with ourselves we are at peace, a word that unites people. The pine cone symbolizes the pineal gland where our spirit is and the understanding of a greater awareness, union of things. Unification divine entity and consciousness so that every observer can channel and understand how he can act better in the world through the integration of each flow in itself. Arch above, portal to enter yourself and know yourself through the sane, awareness.

This artwork is from a limited edition of 20 prints
